{"tid":1407860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 希望大家唔好縮","createTime":"2019-08-04T16:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T11:59:46.000Z","uid":119609,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ef4c336ba89e60ae76d49b84a94a7a39f873a0","tid":1407860,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"政府安然渡過左今次既危機之後<br />\n為左預防類似今次針對警察既思想同行動<br />\n將會通過大量保護警察既法例，例如辱警罪<br />\n導致警權過大<br />\n隨時你藐佢兩野就捉得返差館扣留6個星期<br />\n<br />\n而加仲要加人工<br />\n吸引左一堆yijin仔加入警隊<br />\n然後大部分前線都係yijin仔<br />\n心雄起上黎<br />\n會經常不能控制自己情緒而瘋狂打人<br />\n真係見到警察行過都要忌佢三分<br />\n甚至要大聲講「Good Morning Sir」先俾繼續行<br />\n然後yijin仔就係心入面暗爽<br />\n<br />\n相信收規既時代好快會重臨<br />\n唔講真係以為警察做埋黑社會果份<br />\n投訴都冇人查仲有機會俾人搞返轉頭<br />\n到時唔係話好唔好人好者<br />\nyijin仔見你好哈<br />\n想逗你就逗你<br />\n真係做咩都得<br />\n真正變成<strong>警</strong>察既<strong>世</strong>界<br />\n<br />\n先唔講其他民生同人權問題<br />\n到時可能連自辯既機會都冇<br />\n仲要唔知對面果位係咪真係警察 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係諗起都覺得恐怖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b58e59c7028ab79fe312d1e6dc149c93e9f342","tid":1407860,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b6fdebbe77a60c83300ba9c5513e09f724bd2c","tid":1407860,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eafe82ec26c157d36176eea14d4b72edd841cf4","tid":1407860,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T23:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e85c68f7d5ef7a534ee294418bb46df638b7ea","tid":1407860,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d8f372eac52724de878c60789d6028d73f2225","tid":1407860,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a321593f251bd16a4b6e70c299c466ab3e9d285e","tid":1407860,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a498e7aacac38a8abf6dac0ae8e3e7b0da002018","tid":1407860,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:07:06.000Z","msg":"見到妹妹仔想打電話俾媽媽果條片<br />\n我更加唔想我講既野發生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087dfd8477f45d4e4329f32fa594f6847c81aa37","tid":1407860,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/